rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0003
rows.name:
That Minochi guy..
I don't get why he's tagging along.

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0004
rows.name:
Hmmm, to be honest, I don't know
either. They don't tell us kids anything.

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0005
rows.name:
Maybe I could try and get it out of them
next time we're having a break or
something...

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0007
rows.name:
But...aren't we supposed to be hurrying
to the capital as quickly as possible?

rows.label: campfev11_450_100_msg0009
rows.name:
I guess...that's something else us
kids don't get a say in.
